  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This observational study is conducted in Europe. The trial aims to observe the incidence of
      serious adverse drug reactions in children and adolescents with type 1 diabetes during
      Levemir® treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
